videos.headline: Justyn Ross hauls in TD from back of the end zone
videos.description: D.J. Uiagalelei throws a dime to the back of the end zone for Justyn Ross to haul in for the 7-0 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Justyn Ross hauls in TD from back of the end zone) 2021/09/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Emeka Emezie catches TD with his face mask
videos.description: NC State's Emeka Emezie is able to maintain possession in the end zone by using his facemask to hold on to the catch.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Emeka Emezie catches TD with his face mask) 2021/09/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Devin Carter's TD gives NC State the lead over Clemson
videos.description: Devin Leary's second TD pass of the day is to Devin Carter as NC State takes the lead over Clemson 14-7.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Devin Carter’s TD gives NC State the lead over Clemson) 2021/09/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Uiagalelei's big rush sets up Clemson's tying TD
videos.description: Clemson QB D.J. Uiagalelei scrambles for 37 yards, and on the next play Will Shipley rushes in the game-tying score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Uiagalelei's big rush sets up Clemson's tying TD) 2021/09/25 ESHEET
